## Cryptographic Workflow

```text
                           START
                             │
                             ▼
                 Launch ECC Security System
                             │
                             ▼
                Select an Option from Menu
                             │
                             ▼
        Generate Alice ECC Private Key (.pem)
                             │
                             ▼
         Generate Bob ECC Private Key (.pem)
                             │
                             ▼
       Extract Alice Public Key (.pem)
                             │
                             ▼
        Extract Bob Public Key (.pem)
                             │
                             ▼
     Display & Verify Generated Key Information
                             │
                             ▼
      Alice Generates Shared Secret (ECDH)
                             │
                             ▼
       Bob Generates Shared Secret (ECDH)
                             │
                             ▼
     Compare Both Shared Secret Files (fc /b)
                             │
                  ┌──────────┴──────────┐
                  │                     │
                  ▼                     ▼
             Match Found            No Match
                  │                     │
                  ▼                     ▼
       Secure Channel Ready      Repeat Key Exchange
                  │
                  ▼
          Select File to Protect
                  │
                  ▼
      Generate SHA-256 Hash of File
                  │
                  ▼
   Create Digital Signature (ECDSA)
                  │
                  ▼
 Verify Digital Signature Using Public Key
                  │
          ┌───────┴────────┐
          │                │
          ▼                ▼
   Signature Valid    Signature Invalid
          │                │
          ▼                ▼
     Encrypt File      Stop Process
          │
          ▼
      Decrypt File
          │
          ▼
    Verify File Integrity
          │
          ▼
 Delete Temporary/Generated Files (Optional)
          │
          ▼
             Exit Application
```

### Workflow Summary

1. Launch the ECC Security System.
2. Generate ECC private keys for Alice and Bob.
3. Extract their public keys.
4. Display and verify the generated keys.
5. Perform ECDH key exchange from both sides.
6. Compare the generated shared secrets to confirm successful key exchange.
7. Generate a SHA-256 hash of the file.
8. Digitally sign the file using Alice's private key.
9. Verify the signature using Alice's public key.
10. Encrypt the file.
11. Decrypt the encrypted file.
12. Verify the decrypted file's integrity.
13. Optionally remove temporary/generated files.
14. Exit the application.
